result.execSummary:
The defendant Andrew Dean Chesmore was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Andrew Dean Chesmore is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Andrew Dean Chesmore was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
  • Andrew Dean Chesmore was found guilty of Battery [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
